-- Fillon Ready to Step Down as Prime Minister If Sarkozy Asks, Parisien Says
-- David Whitehouse
-- 2010-07-23T06:00:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/fillon-ready-to-step-down-as-prime-minister-if-sarkozy-asks-parisien-says.html

          
          
             French Prime Minister Francois
Fillon is ready to step down as prime minister if asked by
President Nicolas Sarkozy, Le Parisien newspaper reported,
citing comments made by Fillon last week in Japan.  
 Fillon could stand down between September and the end of
the year, according to the newspaper.  
          
          


  


        